# My recommendation after pasting this
Once you paste this README, do **3 small edits** so it matches your repo perfectly:

## 1) Fix the Streamlit run command if needed
If your actual entry file is:
- `app/0_Home.py` → keep as-is  
- `app/Home.py` or something else → update that line

---

## 2) Update the notebook names section if your actual notebook filenames differ
I intentionally kept that section semi-generic because I don’t want to invent notebook names you may not be using.

---

